text: KWC may refer to: *Karaoke World Championships, a song contest and talent show *Kentucky Wesleyan College, a private Methodist college in Owensboro, Kentucky *Tri-Cities (Ontario), a tri-city area in Ontario, Canada that encompasses Kitchener, Waterloo and Cambridge *King William's College, a school in Castletown, Isle of Man *Kowloon Walled City, a former enclave of Hong Kong *Kyocera Wireless Corporation, a manufacturer of mobile phones
